snippet.title: Mega Man Fan Game - Star Man Upgraded - Casual Playthrough Part 1/3
snippet.description:
This is part 1/3 of a complete playthrough of my fan game, Star Man -Upgraded-. This part just contains the opening.

This is just a casual playthrough showing the game in its entirety; certainly not my best performance as I hadn't played the game in years. 

Hope you enjoy! For more information on Star Man -Upgraded- and a download link, visit my site here: http://blyka.legends-station.com/
